{"tid":2054103,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美5月失業率統計出錯 低估3個百分點","createTime":"2020-06-07T01:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T04:47:19.000Z","uid":150157,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b1032c59f00f9a8b4a8270f55b667fb67ee4e74e","tid":2054103,"uid":150157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"美國昨日公布的就業數據優於預期，其中失業率跌至13.3%，遠勝市場原預期的19%，刺激股市大升。不過，美國勞工統計局其後表示，因收集數據過程出錯，以致低估了4月及5月份失業率，其中5月真實失業率應上調至16.3%。<br />\n<br />\n美國勞工統計局指，統計人員未有將部份停薪留職人士歸類成失業，反而錯誤地歸類為「由於其他原因而沒有上班」，以致失業率出現統計錯誤。當局與人口普查局正調查為什麼會發生這種分類錯誤，並正在採取措施解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n美國勞工統計局續指，4月份失業數據亦出現同一錯誤，經修正後的4月份失業率應由14.7%升至接近20%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2663502/?r=mcsdfb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2663502%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=73ac99ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2663502/?r=mcsdfb2</a>"},{"pid":"f6fd8b8629c2e4f9d881b43ee9ae07182bd6fbac","tid":2054103,"uid":216643,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:28:46.000Z","msg":"痴線，咁離譜<br />\n呢d data 個個月都做㗎啦，擺到明做數"},{"pid":"5a008779f8e75bdce7b8a80183a0bc9260b4ac32","tid":2054103,"uid":288803,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:30:14.000Z","msg":"唔好哄傻淡喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c1662954cee7c87c6506270a4c2266328bb59d","tid":2054103,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:49:55.000Z","msg":"估唔到美國政府都做數"},{"pid":"2d18376c568969d19253a665b3875c7ccc5dab50","tid":2054103,"uid":163493,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:51:55.000Z","msg":"俾淡淡星期日開心吓"},{"pid":"2f937213b6dec3f03bf02845fc23ef2015fc6382","tid":2054103,"uid":1441